    Scope and Contents
Norton, the first superintendent of the Illinois State Archives, discusses her accomplishments in archival work, work and personnel at the Illinois State Archives, and her retirement and travel. The memoir also includes a short interview with Alvin Rountree, who discusses his career under Ms. Norton.1 tape, 90 mins., 16 pp.
Interview by Georgia Rountree, 1972
